<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Cancelled - Sampann</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/aaeb8ebcdf.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .cancel-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #f5c6cb;
        }

        .cancel-container img {
            width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .payment-details {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .payment-details p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #c82333;
        }

        .secondary-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .secondary-button:hover {
            background-color: #5a6268;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="cancel-container">
        <h1>Payment Cancelled</h1>
        <p>We're sorry, <%= user.name %>. Your payment was not completed.</p>
        
        <div class="payment-details">
            <p><strong>Reason:</strong> Payment was cancelled or not successful.</p>
     
        </div>

        <a href="/retry-payment" class="button">Retry Payment</a>
        <a href="/" class="secondary-button">Go to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
